    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2 Class II devices. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the cardiopulmonary bypass use context as described in the requirement and claim documentation. No unresolved weakeners identified.",
